name: Mystery of Ligeia Mare (B&W)
description: 3500x2564px high res scan of analog ink painting, made during the process of painting OBJKT 423820; inspired by the sea "Ligeia Mare", found on Saturn Moon, Titan. Celebrating images from the Cassini Orbiter (NASA JPL Photojournal PIA20021). What is the mystery of the "magic island" there?
